  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ecological Ovens - Eritrea</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project &quot;Ecological ovens&quot; comes from the need to improve the efficiency of the traditional  Eritrean oven- the Mogogo.  Talking of facts, the energy performance of the traditional Mogogo is less then 10% and it is estimated that it consumes 50% of the Eritrean wood.  As it  has no fumes collection system,  these ovens can have serious  health repercussions,  causing respiratory and eyes diseases to people and livestock. The new ovens will provide a sustainable and safe way of cooking.</narrative>
  </description>
